            <title>[CAMEL-19957] camel-jbang - On demand reload is not updating kamelets/routes</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/CAMEL-19957</link>
                <project id="12311211" key="CAMEL">Camel</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;It seems that it does not update if calling on-demand via&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;a href=&quot;http://localhost:8080/q/dev/reload?reload=true&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://localhost:8080/q/dev/reload?reload=true&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;But works if you have file based reloading with --dev&lt;/p&gt;</description>
